skins.shipDescription: Type B3 Mod. 2 cruiser submarine ¨C I-56.
skins.selfIntroduction: I am the 2nd ship of the Type-B Mod. 2 cruiser submarines, I-56. The most noteworthy thing about me... is that I did nothing noteworthy... But there wasn't much I could do at that point anyway...
skins.acquisition: I've been found... I... I'm I-56... Um, if there are any missions I can do by myself, could I get those?
skins.login: Eep?! C-Commander... it's fine to not greet me...
skins.details: Eep?! Oh, C-Commander... did you need something?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, you're always dealing with so many people every day... Amazing... I-I'd never be able to do that...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, being together with you is peaceful and quiet... I can calm down and think about lots of things...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Being athletic like 58 and 19.... err, I mean, 26... would be nice... Eek?! C-Commander? I-I didn't say anything!!
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander, what's the matter? Ah, umm... was I muttering something weird to myself again?!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Eek?! C-Commander... this is just like in that book...?! Ah, um, forget I said that! Sorry...

skins.shipDescription: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...
skins.acquisition: School... is pretty nice. I can quietly stay in this corner and mind my own business...
skins.details: The other kids often post all kinds of pictures onto social media from their phones... Commander, you can also take a look.
skins.secretaryIdle1: At school, you can see a completely different side of people. It can be pretty interesting...
skins.secretaryIdle2: I've received invitations from several clubs before... but I still prefer to watch others from a distance.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Don't worry, Commander. I'm enjoying my time at school.
skins.secretaryTouch: ... What's the matter, Commander? Oh, I was just watching that couple over there walking to school together...
